{"tid":1974749,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一蚊 Joe 和一班《東張西望》工作人員涉違反禁聚令，圍堆一齊隊酒！","createTime":"2020-04-16T05:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T05:23:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb53aa6bc823675bd477133f43c0be05a9de76f","tid":1974749,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"港府連月來對武漢疫情的處理被外界轟「慢九拍」，但另一方面某些政策又倉卒執行。上月底實施的「禁聚令」，規定4人以上，不得在公眾地方聚集，食肆除了規限4人一枱外，枱與枱之間亦必須最少有1.5米距離，不過連日來「禁聚令」存有不少漏洞，除了警方和食環處的執法被指有「大細超」之嫌，而遭人連番詬病外，不少食店為不想得失食客，即使食飯人數超過最高限制，亦選擇隻眼開隻眼閉。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200414/large/1586865408_932f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200414%2Flarge%2F1586865408_932f.jpg&h=a9edf26a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n日前下午約5時，育有一仔一女的大台一蚊Joe（游莨維），被《蘋果》發現和一班《東張西望》工作人員在九龍城一泰國食肆出現。當日他們約有7、8個人，浩浩蕩蕩走入食肆最入面的枱中，然後落單叫嘢食。現場所見，一蚊Joe和工作人員最初都肯守規矩，分開兩枱坐，每枱只坐3至4人，不過當啤酒、小吃來到時，他們暢飲一輪便開始放鬆起來，有人走過隔鄰枱打牙齩傾偈。到酒過三巡後，眾人身心便開始變得鬆懈，開始起哄圍埋一堆，邊飲酒邊猜枚，有人在未有戴上口罩的情況下，熱情地搭着友人膊頭吹水咬耳仔，笑聲、說話聲傳遍整間食店。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200416/TXNJ4AJ7C75K5ULFWFBYQFTVPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200416%2FTXNJ4AJ7C75K5ULFWFBYQFTVPA%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=c02d1ed3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200416%2FTXNJ4AJ7C75K5ULFWFBYQFTVPA%2F&h=2eaa3569\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200416/TXNJ4AJ7C75K5ULFWFBYQFTVPA/</a>"},{"pid":"227cc586fff3935350d51d39ee0b2732e1eef6de","tid":1974749,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"雖然一蚊Joe等人違規，超過法定的4人「禁聚令」，不過食店職員卻沒有上前阻止，反而和他們傾埋一份。直到埋單一刻，飲到面紅紅的一蚊Joe，打算拿起賬單出櫃枱埋單，結果被另一工作人員搶先一步。飲飽食醉的眾人，在門外仍未捨得散，再圍爐煲煙一輪，才分乘兩架車離去。"},{"pid":"ddc3588ed2e22bb18c0c4b062f6b4e248224afe1","tid":1974749,"uid":349872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"TVB嘅人有特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38d356f322fc5e4ade26e959bc6e815c434aa32","tid":1974749,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"一蚊Joe他們最初都守規矩，分開兩張枱食飯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200414/large/1586865408_16bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200414%2Flarge%2F1586865408_16bc.jpg&h=cfb59779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過飲飽食醉後後，就索性坐埋一齊，在未有戴上口罩下猜枚、吹水。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200414/large/1586865408_3d7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200414%2Flarge%2F1586865408_3d7d.jpg&h=183875ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03c85593d248c59218ffdb0c58d27ca7e6b59526","tid":1974749,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qr3qNCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQr3qNCw.png&h=d56da67d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdkAqpe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdkAqpe.png&h=d7cd4d97&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}